="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：Samuel Corum/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 24px;" /&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;据称，&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;美国财政部的技术团队&lt;/strong&gt;正在寻求&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/5AxDaOduXT9xCXaW9642zB3hDS_1AgD5j0wu4cZUiU5LHGApRGyCErZF8SVIi8DlUmQGgzRGNjC4v_uSniZd-ZRGsyNC22pHRCpCGJhG7vDun_2ty16ISIcJlzfbfuz7-b_mOZzsx7aDiwcmLEDTmRUvt7P5HCaaelLosBB3vpglAaelGbQT_sCVgPRUWaWCP7d-INom2ngRLZfZu6d_apWR9vRwz-bPnwGWMlK5LKyYoHgOGf4uKpkp1DUH4iKQ6cYZhBB1B8puokli52PofFMEWKM6fl_2FYqUtXQn2Kmol8Iq81VOBa_JuB07IZ66tRoFNTulbBoi08fWEFgPy3VLUSXe5gpyO-Asm-ftkrGFn_T_en9QUdPZFH1ofJtoDSJhAxZ-Uqdlwl8YSQ3K6X-G5prjfJXjZm5GAKFQsixWZfFqgep9i1DsqKIQ8s46Yfz0dSX8q2xy4R6Y0QEJKh5RSU0K_SQPRdK0or1lXgullK2uwp6-KFkA9CjRITZ-bgT7rQ/pHAykVt8lxwsqKK4YQtu4eVqfyUjL0pc/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="美国财政部寻求利用 Anthropic 的神话来寻找缺陷"&gt;访问 Anthropic 的 Mythos 人工智能模型，&lt;/a&gt;以便开始寻找漏洞。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;财政部首席信息官 Sam Corcos 的目标是最快在本周获得该模型的访问权，Anthropic 已将该模型发布给有限数量的机构。美国财政部长斯科特·贝森特和美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔上周&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/9sGfyfM1ZvY9r8Kx0dAfg-Qek0pxH2wr3XGYr18V-x1Djma84G_dg-i_nCCGmwXkV-esE6aDn3qeDmZUzZTiB-dUBkR625zlJj25RG_aMYOPYeTSbhCqbOp2HiPzvoGQQXXZ3UblbOdsFFVaEXAE1QLqH7DBFGhBoUvRIO1h7PCuD38svYxLBKSdxefp5ZN2b2YhQvekB3-fU2EpAP_j0Gv_7zZlM-eh2Zqlbp3Rq8GEu5dsOx3GSn3fvkq4YWXksxoXuFcLTg-5jV87bRVInvOlFLWl3O0k6ick-Ou3tDUgphNFrlm4Pn-w7CokudLUhaz8G37jwyaFM85nJbAgD_C18FWgfwGFe_5RXXVvp1xFK4lYCVQ_3pZqhpfVkZTcz4hrGhwK7jCxO7eu2sKOU7Ynfvipp7rGT2v9aMaN9E1qrQfWfL3CRAGP6rHz6JV5K2hx3k5oJRSTEVni25lwYA5ohMvArMwnqHbC3PIZ8lnOIINjywkgIbbwq2zwZ2AMYAY6BEtrpdy4Pjkadw/0B-92oHtjD1BLkZsSMB5Oi18hFOW102v/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="人择模型恐慌引发紧急警告，鲍威尔向银行首席执行官发出警告"&gt;召集华尔街领导人&lt;/a&gt;召开紧急会议，担心 Mythos 将迎来一个网络风险更大的时代。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 24px;" /&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;迪士尼将裁员 1,000 人&lt;/strong&gt;，这是新任首席执行官乔什·达马罗 (Josh D&amp;#39;Amaro) 领导下的首次大规模裁员。虽然解雇是在全公司范围内进行的， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/pGLoff3UP3edczpINKn3-ojyBsErbiW9TRyv5uTQrTOTFQxKtJR1fd6-oq23baMsgS7yyA7zgwELNpavF4lKjY6Olk599nXDRApm7QnJH_VM4ttipCgLlXgC9Wr-4Nkxz1_wq8LiUbuP4PVux7DjTCOCZweVOFIWDG0JLaoMtl5PSwf7NIvmsL2Q29dbg2YsdJLHXblIHqbaZm_v8WbIUBtPUEPui4hbV08pobESS3Rrm9iXnTy3IfeTeGFgRpdIDwd8iVXNuG-e0JdAhV0ctnwq_lwAaIVHrp-cI3RpQU2Mh8lW12Mc-IUe-bAtTkYTqgqNECpjrOrrEGL2_0uxQIg96-EjD98ggvQJVY1tVEEYkOb5JLDw18sf2C7R_FiYnhM_2HgKYkzzqfTVSicUglEI_vKEjah1IFOMIcKX971WJtnoLttKJJfXce2R5nVf9ayqrGePcnNhGT3uH2NNEkIBSe8SgbaE-9MqZGqhpH_p7bWnrYJLn-GVkydQKzk81g/jy5De1HcAmkH_4ibjo9Sxc5m_GDwGDqQ/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="迪士尼在新任首席执行官的领导下首次裁员 1,000 人"&gt;但营销部门的员工受到的打击尤其严重&lt;/a&gt;，该部门正在整合到阿萨德·阿亚兹 (Asad Ayaz) 的领导下，阿萨德·阿亚兹于 1 月份被任命为首席营销和品牌官。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;自 2023 年以来，迪士尼已解雇了 8,000 多名员工，而这一轮裁员是在迪士尼进行的。尽管如此，这一数字仅是迪士尼截至 2025 财年末 231,000 名员工的一小部分。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 24px;" /&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;亚马逊同意以约&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/R3X91l37_kwQ6DuLkCRPvcFDRPBOBCxsvNk7wTYHBJpNCbJkCDtyJmGYvL_LCMQY9C-Np_E3aIaZqYGDJjDG63XeNofGDCQLwPa9_kEKlPgo5JXUn9p3Oh5cR4OPmL21U4Ulh92Ix6XwcmsnIHP1-DEpSieWh1mBJmA9MsiTTpuUsfHUc8IdfSYP06WjTY7xM1r25AhHfC3wvL48jJdSnSLSuHQ0HhD_WU-yMBwX82V3EqIJe-Vdyu4BlhJD3AaCfCoet5Bkipf1jpE8fcDrkPm1h--t3IfUSVFJIwCpIoHEqQew_FO_BDrhD_n1EAoi8rbHxhiiNjRFgEAk4K_iZMLmCYrg4f1A5QFZ6_A20Jit7or-1DZ7XD6AnyTyzIE2f6tnsHbKPP4rRs5i7-nZUoqoAsTFQ6wgmMRMHMHmtGB2cDqzUElEP6HjE8egK2uV2u-LE4-eXkCap4TOM87DqmuFcgVvVCBitw8A0ZcuLyZSHsIxxNuNgHPGShlzg4ou5X5M03hdnefDGePBUvGT6SQ/EE_WMJNZ5Y0jUd-53Ur8U_gAVOPWiPey/1